INSTALL

git clone https://github.com/nevesenin/open_last_commit.git
ln -s ~/open_last_commit/olc.pl ~/bin/olc

EXAMPLES

olc

	open last commited files and working directory with sublime text 2

olc -n

	open last commited files without working directory with sublime text 2

ols -n -e 'vi'

	open last commited files without working directory with vi

olc -n -e 'vi' -s b00f831a88dd8c72ae12efae8f98652e23d5c2b3

	open files from commit b00f831a88dd8c72ae12efae8f98652e23d5c2b3 without working directory with vi